## Recommended Execution Order

### Phase 1: File Moves (Do First)
Order: Part 1 → Part 5

1. Move `numbering_*.rb` files to `wordprocessingml/`
2. Move `styles_configuration.rb` to `wordprocessingml/`
3. Move `styles/*.rb` to `wordprocessingml/styles/`
4. Move `color_scheme.rb`, `font_scheme.rb`, `format_scheme.rb` to `drawingml/`
5. Update module declarations in moved files
