2. Create `spec/uniword/drawingml/` directory
3. Move WordprocessingML-related specs
4. Move DrawingML-related specs
5. Move integration tests to `spec/integration/`
6. Run tests to verify all pass

### Phase 3: Spec Fixes (Do Third)
Order: Part 4

1. Fix `Uniword::Style` references → `Uniword::Wordprocessingml::Style`
2. Fix boolean default expectations
3. Remove/fix visitor pattern tests
4. Fix remaining test failures
5. Run full test suite

